Re: Brief question about a name...
by TokonatsuHana » Sun 07.03.2011 7:51 pm Thanks so much! That's a relief, lol... I was always worried that my putting 常 and 夏 together into one word wasn't actually grammatically correct, so I'm really glad that it's legitimate It's just that they were giving me a such hard time about it I wanted to know if it even made sense in the first place XDAnd that's even better to know that 花 fit's comfortably afterward with no need for a の because the romanji spelling with a "no" in it would just look confusing to people who don't know any Japanese. Thanks again for taking the time to read and reply to this thread, I really appreciate it! ^_^
